
To run the cat.swift program, do:
swift cat.swift

You can select the site where you run the program by editing the swift.conf file:

# To run on just your local machine
site=local

# To run on a static cloud setup, for the tutorial
site=cloud-static

# To run with dynamic coasters
site=aws



Download and setup the sample dataset from gutenberg.org :
wget http://www.gutenberg.org/files/4300/4300.zip
unzip 4300.zip
mkdir -p input
mv 4300.txt input
rm 4300.zip


